text: The Renault Safrane was a car produced by Renault. It replaced the Renault 25 in 1992, facelifted in 1995 and was produced until 1998. It was replaced by the Renault Vel Satis in 2000. == Engines == === Petrol === * 2.0 79 kW (107 hp) * 2.0 12V 103 kW (140 hp) * 2.0 16V 100 kW (136 hp) * 2.2 79 kW (107 hp) * 2.2 12V 101 kW (137 hp) * 2.5 20V 121 kW (165 hp) * 3.0 123 kW (167 hp) * 3.0 24V 143 kW (194 hp) * 3.0 Biturbo 193 kW (262 hp) === Diesel === * 2.1 dT 65 kW (88 hp) * 2.2 dT 83 kW (113 hp) * 2.5 dT 83 kW (113 hp) Safrane Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles
